#ADVISORY | 𝙏𝙝𝙚 𝙚𝙭𝙘𝙞𝙩𝙚𝙢𝙚𝙣𝙩’𝙨 𝙘𝙤𝙤𝙠𝙞𝙣𝙜… 𝙨𝙩𝙖𝙮 𝙩𝙪𝙣𝙚𝙙! 🍳✨

We’re putting the finishing touches on the 𝗙𝗘𝗨 𝗔𝗻𝘁𝗶-𝗕𝘂𝗹𝗹𝘆𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝗖𝗼𝗿𝗲 𝗚𝗿𝗼𝘂𝗽 𝗘𝘅𝗲𝗰𝘂𝘁𝗶𝘃𝗲 𝗖𝗼𝗺𝗺𝗶𝘁𝘁𝗲𝗲 acceptance emails to make sure every application gets the attention it deserves.

Think of it as letting the flavors meld before the big reveal, 𝘆𝗼𝘂𝗿 𝗰𝗵𝗮𝗻𝗰𝗲 𝘁𝗼 𝗯𝗲 𝗽𝗮𝗿𝘁 𝗼𝗳 𝘀𝗼𝗺𝗲𝘁𝗵𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝗺𝗲𝗮𝗻𝗶𝗻𝗴𝗳𝘂𝗹 𝗶𝘀 𝗮𝗹𝗺𝗼𝘀𝘁 𝗵𝗲𝗿𝗲! While you wait, keep that energy going, because we can’t wait to see all the amazing things you’ll bring to the group.

The acceptance emails have now been rescheduled to 𝗦𝗲𝗽𝘁𝗲𝗺𝗯𝗲𝗿 𝟭𝟵, 𝟮𝟬𝟮𝟱. The countdown might have a tiny pause, but the impact you’ll make starts from day one! 🌟

#ABCGoldenIsabela
#ISABCG

Caption by Libradette Aranas

#ADVISORY | 𝙏𝙝𝙚 𝙚𝙭𝙘𝙞𝙩𝙚𝙢𝙚𝙣𝙩’𝙨 𝙘𝙤𝙤𝙠𝙞𝙣𝙜… 𝙨𝙩𝙖𝙮 𝙩𝙪𝙣𝙚𝙙! 🍳✨

We’re putting the finishing touches on the 𝗙𝗘𝗨 𝗔𝗻𝘁𝗶-𝗕𝘂𝗹𝗹𝘆𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝗖𝗼𝗿𝗲 𝗚𝗿𝗼𝘂𝗽 𝗘𝘅𝗲𝗰𝘂𝘁𝗶𝘃𝗲 𝗖𝗼𝗺𝗺𝗶𝘁𝘁𝗲𝗲 acceptance emails to make sure every application gets the attention it deserves.

Think of it as letting the flavors meld before the big reveal, 𝘆𝗼𝘂𝗿 𝗰𝗵𝗮𝗻𝗰𝗲 𝘁𝗼 𝗯𝗲 𝗽𝗮𝗿𝘁 𝗼𝗳 𝘀𝗼𝗺𝗲𝘁𝗵𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝗺𝗲𝗮𝗻𝗶𝗻𝗴𝗳𝘂𝗹 𝗶𝘀 𝗮𝗹𝗺𝗼𝘀𝘁 𝗵𝗲𝗿𝗲! While you wait, keep that energy going, because we can’t wait to see all the amazing things you’ll bring to the group.

The acceptance emails have now been rescheduled to 𝗦𝗲𝗽𝘁𝗲𝗺𝗯𝗲𝗿 𝟭𝟵, 𝟮𝟬𝟮𝟱. The countdown might have a tiny pause, but the impact you’ll make starts from day one! 🌟

#ABCGoldenIsabela
#ISABCG

Caption by Libradette Aranas

We’re putting the finishing touches on the 𝗙𝗘𝗨 𝗔𝗻𝘁𝗶-𝗕𝘂𝗹𝗹𝘆𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝗖𝗼𝗿𝗲 𝗚𝗿𝗼𝘂𝗽 𝗘𝘅𝗲𝗰𝘂𝘁𝗶𝘃𝗲 𝗖𝗼𝗺𝗺𝗶𝘁𝘁𝗲𝗲 acceptance emails to make sure every application gets the attention it deserves.

Think of it as letting the flavors meld before the big reveal, 𝘆𝗼𝘂𝗿 𝗰𝗵𝗮𝗻𝗰𝗲 𝘁𝗼 𝗯𝗲 𝗽𝗮𝗿𝘁 𝗼𝗳 𝘀𝗼𝗺𝗲𝘁𝗵𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝗺𝗲𝗮𝗻𝗶𝗻𝗴𝗳𝘂𝗹 𝗶𝘀 𝗮𝗹𝗺𝗼𝘀𝘁 𝗵𝗲𝗿𝗲! While you wait, keep that energy going, because we can’t wait to see all the amazing things you’ll bring to the group.

The acceptance emails have now been rescheduled to 𝗦𝗲𝗽𝘁𝗲𝗺𝗯𝗲𝗿 𝟭𝟵, 𝟮𝟬𝟮𝟱. The countdown might have a tiny pause, but the impact you’ll make starts from day one! 🌟
